Header":false,"content":" <b>Insert butterfly whisk.<b> Place cream in mixing bowl and, without measuring cup and without setting a time, whip <b>speed 3<b> until soft peaks form, watching carefully to avoid over-whipping. Transfer to bowl with sabayon and gently fold together. Fill each pastry case to the top with cream mixture. Refrigerate for one hour. Garnish with fresh figs before serving.","step":8}],"usefulItems":"baking paper, cling film, round pastry cutter, fork, baking tray, tartlet tins (Ø 8 cm), rolling pin, baking beans, refrigerator, oven","id":"r175666","imageLink":"https:\/\/1.bp.blogspot.com\/-RguyKmL2yIo\/XZWp-dyeWPI\/AAAAAAAAfRY\/ShKMOtN0J7cjZjiDwh-Q6u-rkrMEcajTgCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_9-PrJ55pjj0STSL1.png","title":"Limoncello Tarts","ingredients":[{"isHeader":true,"content":"Ingredients"},{"isHeader":true,"content":"Walnut and Rosemary Pastry"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"80 g walnuts, chopped"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"40 g brown sugar"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"1 pinch fine sea salt"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"1 Tbsp fresh rosemary, leaves only"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"230 g wholemeal flour"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"120 g unsalted butter, diced"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"1 large egg"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"wholemeal flour, for dusting"},{"isHeader":true,"content":"Limoncello Filling and Topping"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"80 g sugar"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"1 Tbsp lemon zest"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"80 g limoncello"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"60 g lemon juice, freshly squeezed (1-2 lemons)"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"1 large egg"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"4 egg yolks, from large eggs"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"200 g whipping cream"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"8 fresh figs, cut in eighths"}],"nutrition":["per 1 portion","2244 kJ \/ 536 kcal","10 g","44 g","32 g"],"hintsAndTricks":["Serve the limoncello tarts with seasonal fresh fruit such as strawberries, raspberries or peaches."],"b